CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 6, 1956, pg. 11, reads: "Get-Acquainted Party - "Size, please," were the words spoken by Delta sorors at the get-acquainted party at the Centre Ave. YWCA. Admission was charged according to the size of shoe the person wore.  Did you know so many people wore sizes four and five? - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Delta Sigma Theta members and guests, including woman in center registering at table in Centre Avenue YWCA for Get Acquainted Party
